#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.60"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.60:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.60:0.2"
msgid "6. Puññābhisandavagga "
msgstr "6. Overflowing Merit "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: gihisāmīcipaṭipadāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.60:0.3"
msgid "60. Gihisāmīcisutta "
msgstr "60. Lay Practice "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.65, sc1
msgctxt "an4.60:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ bhagavā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the householder Anāthapiṇḍika went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to one side. The Buddha said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.60:2.1"
msgid "“Catūhi kho, gahapati, dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako gihisāmīcipaṭipadaṃ paṭipanno hoti yasopaṭilābhiniṃ saggasaṃvattanikaṃ. "
msgstr "“Householder, when a noble disciple does four things they are practicing appropriately for a layperson, which brings fame and leads to heaven. "

msgctxt "an4.60:2.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an4.60:2.3"
msgid "Idha, gahapati, ariyasāvako bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paccupaṭṭhito hoti cīvarena, bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paccupaṭṭhito hoti piṇḍapātena, bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paccupaṭṭhito hoti senāsanena, bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paccupaṭṭhito hoti gilānappaccayabhesajjaparikkhārena. "
msgstr "It’s when a noble disciple serves the mendicant Saṅgha with robes, alms-food, lodgings, and medicines and supplies for the sick. "

msgctxt "an4.60:2.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, gahapati, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato ariyasāvako gihisāmīcipaṭipadaṃ paṭipanno hoti yasopaṭilābhiniṃ saggasaṃvattanikanti. "
msgstr "When a noble disciple does these four things they are practicing appropriately for a layperson, which brings fame and leads to heaven. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.60:3.1"
msgid "Gihisāmīcipaṭipadaṃ, "
msgstr "Those who are astute practice the way "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:3.2"
msgid "paṭipajjanti paṇḍitā; "
msgstr "that’s appropriate for laypeople. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:3.3"
msgid "Sammaggate sīlavante, "
msgstr "They provide those who are ethical "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:3.4"
msgid "cīvarena upaṭṭhitā. "
msgstr "and on the right path with robes, "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.60:4.1"
msgid "Piṇḍapātasayanena, "
msgstr "alms-food, lodgings, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:4.2"
msgid "Gilānappaccayena ca; "
msgstr "and supplies for the sick. "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:4.3"
msgid "Tesaṃ divā ca ratto ca, "
msgstr "Their merit always grows "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:4.4"
msgid "Sadā puññaṃ pavaḍḍhati; "
msgstr "by day and by night. "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: Saggañca kamatiṭṭhānaṃ → saggañca kamati ṭhānaṃ (pts1) | saggañca sappatiṭṭhānaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an4.60:4.5"
msgid "Saggañca kamatiṭṭhānaṃ, "
msgstr "They pass on to a place in heaven, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:4.6"
msgid "Kammaṃ katvāna bhaddakan”ti. "
msgstr "having done excellent deeds.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.60:4.7"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.60:4.8"
msgid "Puññābhisandavaggo paṭhamo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.60:5.1"
msgid "Dve puññābhisandā dve ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:5.2"
msgid "saṃvāsā samajīvino; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:5.3"
msgid "Suppavāsā sudatto ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an4.60:5.4"
msgid "bhojanaṃ gihisāmicīti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
